  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EventHandler  
    EventHandlerErrorResponse  
    ExternalEventHandler
    The base External Event Handler that can be orchestrated The implementors of this handler will implement this
    ExternalEventHandlerErrorResponse
    The use of this interface would be in the following scenario: You already have a user-developed External Event handler You wish to throw an exception in your Event Handler (based on some error in your processing) You also wish to control which error response is sent back based on your thrown exception
